                                    </span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-xs-6 all-to-none" style="text-align:right;">
                                    <span class="all-to-none" id="max_mileage">
                                        100000 Mile
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-4">
                            <div class="col-xs-12 slider_bar_container_title">
